:::{"id":"f0f4c83e-0bc4-4211-94f3-e70f618ca6a3","title":{"en":"Hanazakari no Niwa"},"availableTranslatedLanguages":["tr"],"description":{"en":"Masaki Tachibana leaves home in order to escape an oppressive existence with his father. He shows up at his grandfather's house, uninvited, and decides to live there. A garden that he saw in dream; his grandfather and his bodyguard, Harada; an old mansion inhabited by a beautiful, strong-willed girl…  
  
At this point, the curtain rises on a mysterious drama of love and hate!  
  
Also included in this volume is the story called Love Letter:  
Kagawa recounts his meeting and becoming friends with Okada when he is introduced to Okada's fiancee. He is reborn after 100 years in the body of a child. ……What? The Mount Hua Sect has fallen? What kind of nonsense is that!?

Sekte Hwasan hancur?!"","it":"Chung Myung, il 13esimo discepolo della Mount Hua Sec, uno dei 3 grandi spadaccini, Il santo della spada del fiore del pruno sconfisse Chun Ma, colui che ha portato distruzione e caos nel mondo.
Dopo la battaglia, esala il suo ultimo respiro in cima alla montagna del quartiere generale della Heavenly Demon Sect.

Ma, dopo 100 anni rinasce nel corpo di un bambino.
....Cosa? La mont Hua Sec è scomparsa? Cosa sta succedendo?","ko":"대 화산파 13대 제자.천하삼대검수 매화검존 청명.
천하를 혼란에 빠뜨린 고금제일마 천마의 목을 치고 십만대산의 정상에서 영면.
백 년의 시간을 뛰어넘어 아이의 몸으로 다시 살아나다.
......뭐? 화산이 망해? 이게 뭔 개소리야!?","ru":"13-й ученик великой школы Хуашань, один из трех величайших фехтовальщиков в мире - благородный клинок цветущей сливы Чхон Мён.
Последним ударом клинка он убивает Чхонма, повергшего весь мир в хаос, и погибает на вершине горы из голов тысячи демонов.
А спустя 100 лет он перерождается в теле ребенка, чтобы возродить из пепла некогда одну из самых великих, но ныне всеми забытую школу Мурима - Хуашань.
Цветки сливы рано или поздно опадают. Однако когда приходит холодная зима, а за ней - весна, слива распускается в своем полном великолепии.","th":"สงครามกับเทพมารสิ้นสุดแล้ว และความตายที่ไม่อาจเลี่ยงได้กำลังคืบคลานมาหาข้าเช่นกัน ข้าผู้เป็นศิษย์รุ่น 13 แห่งฮวาซานได้ปลิดชีพเทพมารที่สั่นคลอนทั่วพิภพลงได้ในที่สุด และสิ้นสุดอายุขัยบนจุดสูงสุดของยอดเขา ...แต่พอข้าลืมตาขึ้นอีกที กลับกลายเป็นยาจกไร้กำลัง นี่ข้ากลับมาเกิดใหม่เป็นขอทานหรือนี่?!","zh":"剑尊大战魔尊后同归于尽！
百年后竟重生成柔弱孩童？
男主清明前世是闻名江湖的华山派梅花剑尊，耗尽全力消灭了武林魔头“天魔”，最终与其同归于尽。但他却在百年后重生成了一个落魄小乞丐，并且保留着前世所有记忆。而在现世，曾是江湖名派的“华山派”已经没落至无人知晓的地步，清明得知这一事实后不能接受。当他找到华山后，发现门派已油尽灯枯。但清明仍然还记得百年前门派的道义和武学精神，他很不甘心，于是以孩童之身重新拜入华山派门下。但入门后他才知道，原来门派没落竟与前世自己和天魔大战有关！孩童之身的他该如何重振门派雄风呢？","zh-hk":"華山派梅花劍尊青明與天魔同歸於盡後，再次醒來發現百年後的華山派竟已不屬於九派一幫，震驚之下他立志要讓華山派重振當年盛極一時的威風!"},"links":{"al":"132144","ap":"return-of-the-blossoming-blade","engtl":"https://www.webtoons.com/en/action/return-of-the-blossoming-blade/list?title_no=2849","kt":"hwasangwihwan","mal":"146878","mu":"179258","nu":"return-of-mount-hua-sect","raw":"https://comic.naver.com/webtoon/list?titleId=769209"},"originalLanguage":"ko","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"0bc90acb-ccc1-44ca-a34a-b9f3a73259d0","name":{"en":"Reincarnation"}},{"id":"391b0423-d847-456f-aff0-8b0cfc03066b","name":{"en":"Action"}},{"id":"3e2b8dae-350e-4ab8-a8ce-016e844b9f0d","name":{"en":"Long Strip"}},{"id":"4d32cc48-9f00-4cca-9b5a-a839f0764984","name":{"en":"Comedy"}},{"id":"799c202e-7daa-44eb-9cf7-8a3c0441531e","name":{"en":"Martial Arts"}},{"id":"87cc87cd-a395-47af-b27a-93258283bbc6","name":{"en":"Adventure"}},{"id":"cdc58593-87dd-415e-bbc0-2ec27bf404cc","name":{"en":"Fantasy"}},{"id":"e197df38-d0e7-43b5-9b09-2842d0c326dd","name":{"en":"Web Comic"}},{"id":"f4122d1c-3b44-44d0-9936-ff7502c39ad3","name":{"en":"Adaptation"}},{"id":"f5ba408b-0e7a-484d-8d49-4e9125ac96de","name":{"en":"Full Color"}}]}

Large earrings in her ears,
Dark red lipstick on her lips.

Kanzaki Yuki is a college student who wears a strong fashion style.
Despite her strong appearance,

But recently she found a ghost she just can't ignore:
Aizawa Honami, ex-classmate and ex-member of the famous idol group De:LPhinus, hanging around school from some lingering attachment.

Still, no matter what ghost it is, Michi's not getting involved.
Though while she steels her heart, her eyes keep coming back to Honami's bizarre antics and passionate fanservice...(?)","es-la":"Michi, maldecida para siempre con la capacidad de ver fantasmas, finge que no puede verlos precisamente porque quiere evitarlos a toda costa.

Pero recientemente se encontró con un fantasma que no puede ignorar: Aizawa Honami, excompañera de clase y ex miembro del famoso grupo de Idols "De:LPhinus", quien también era compañera de clase, comenzó a aparecer en el salón de clases por algún motivo.

Aun así, no importa qué fantasmas sean, Michi no quiere involucrarse. Mientras protege su corazón, sus ojos continúan observando las payasadas y el fanservice (?) de Honami.","id":"Michi, diganggu selamanya oleh kemampuannya untuk melihat hantu, berpura-pura seperti dia tidak bisa melihat mereka untuk menghindari mereka bagaimanaoun itu.

Tapi baru-baru ini dia menemukan hantu yang tidak bisa dia abaikan:
Aizawa Honami, mantan teman sekelas dan mantan anggota grup idola terkenal De:LPhinus, berkeliaran di sekolah karena keterikatan yang masih melekat.

Tetap saja, tidak peduli hantu apa itu, Michi tidak terlibat.
Meskipun saat dia menguatkan hatinya, matanya terus kembali ke kejenakaan aneh dan fanservice Honami yang penuh gairah...(?)","pt-br":"Michi, amaldiçoada para sempre pela habilidade de enxergar fantasmas, finge que não pode vê-los justamente porque quer evitá-los a todo custo.

Mas recentemente ela encontrou um fantasma que não pode ignorar:
Aizawa Honami, ex-colega de classe e ex-membro do famoso grupo de idols De:LPhinus, fica perambulando em torno da escola com ainda algum tipo de vínculo.

Ainda assim, não importa o que fantasmas são, Michi não quer se envolver.
Enquanto ela blinda seu coração, seus olhos continuam a observar as travessuras e fanservide de Honami."},"links":{"al":"151909","amz":"https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B0BZQ2VX6F","bw":"series/403138","ebj":"https://ebookjapan.yahoo.co.jp/books/751492/","kt":"mietemasu-yo-aizawa-san","mal":"150928","mu":"bvqavvw","raw":"https://www.comic-valkyrie.com/aizawasan/"},"originalLanguage":"ja","publicationDemographic":"seinen","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"3bb26d85-09d5-4d2e-880c-c34b974339e9","name":{"en":"Ghosts"}},{"id":"423e2eae-a7a2-4a8b-ac03-a8351462d71d","name":{"en":"Romance"}},{"id":"4d32cc48-9f00-4cca-9b5a-a839f0764984","name":{"en":"Comedy"}},{"id":"a3c67850-4684-404e-9b7f-c69850ee5da6","name":{"en":"Girls' Love"}},{"id":"caaa44eb-cd40-4177-b930-79d3ef2afe87","name":{"en":"School Life"}},{"id":"cdad7e68-1419-41dd-bdce-27753074a640","name":{"en":"Horror"}},{"id":"eabc5b4c-6aff-42f3-b657-3e90cbd00b75","name":{"en":"Supernatural"}}]}

:::{"id":"f13603d1-2ce6-44d2-96be-fd9902bd04b3","title":{"en":"Winter Romantic B\u0026B"},"altTitles":[{"en":"Fuyu no Roman Minshuku"},{"en":"Winter at a Romantic Guest House"},{"en":"Winter Romantic B \u0026 B"},{"en":"Winter Romantic B and B"},{"en":"冬の浪漫民宿"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["pl"],"description":{"en":"Yuu is an energetic girl who's trying her best to keep close to her boyfriend Roku, a student from another school and very busy with club activities. When he has to be away for winter's vacations, will her efforts still be enough?  \n  \nITALIANO:
column7: Sono tre mesi che Yuu e Roku escono insieme e fra poco arriverà il compleanno di Roku. Yuu ha già pensato al regalo: ha vinto un fantastico soggiorno in un B\u0026B, però Roku le rovina i piani. Il ragazzo decide di partecipare alle attività invernali del suo club di nuoto e quindi trascorre con loro le vacanze invernali in un B\u0026B di un suo senpai. Yuu però non si arrende e riesce a partire con lui ed i suoi compagni, ma una volta lì, dovrà vedersela con una rivale in amore, del tutto sleale!

:::{"id":"f16c425a-6a46-4f50-bb65-1050855cccb2","title":{"en":"Roelin's Path to the Future"},"altTitles":[{"ko":"로엘린은 미래를 걷는다"},{"ko-ro":"Loelline Miraereul Geonneunda"},{"en":"Loelline Seizes the Future"},{"en":"Roelin Walks the Future"},{"ja":"ロエリンは未来を歩く"},{"zh":"预知未来的洛琳"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["en"],"description":{"en":"Roelin Deaz, the daughter of Count Deaz, who is supporting the family that is in debt due to her father's business failure. While struggling to raise the family on the verge of collapse, Roelin has an accident that almost killed her one day. This as an opportunity, she remembers the past when she was the high priest of the temple of night and darkness, which has now disappeared, and gains the power of her previous life, which is the power to know the future through dreams-! After accepting her change, Roelin uses her previous life's experiences and abilities to work hard to revive her family. Then one day, through a dream, she sees someone's death. That person is none other than the protector of the empire, Duke Dante van Benerite, who is called the Knight of Brilliance?! Roelin learns of his miserable future and becomes conflicted...! What will Roelin do?

---
One day, a near-death experience causes Loelline Deaz to remember her past life, awakening the power to see the future through her dreams. However, there is one vision in particular that weighs on her the most— she foresees the murder of the empire's hero, Duke Dante van Benerit! Loelline is the only one who can save the duke, but as she gets closer to uncovering the conspiracy behind his demise, she realizes that her past may have more to do with the grim future than she could've ever dreamed...

:::{"id":"f1889360-c765-4f2b-9ab4-d69c7e74e22f","title":{"en":"Mako and Rumi and Chii"},"altTitles":[{"en":"Mako & Rumi & Chii"},{"ja":"マコとルミとチイ"},{"ja-ro":"Mako to Rumi to Chii"}],"lastChapter":"51","availableTranslatedLanguages":["en"],"description":{"en":"This Manga deals with parenting, depicting the daily lives of mangaka Ohsamu Tetsuro, who strongly resembles Tezuka Osamu himself, and his family.  
  
The story begins with the birth of his first son. The son is named Makoto (nicknamed Mako) and grows to be a healthy 2 year-old, basking in the love of his orderly mother and careless father. The son is followed by two daughters named Rumiko (nicknamed Rumi) and Chiiko (nicknamed Chii). This story focuses on the increasing hustle and bustle inside the Ohsamu family.

Also includes the 4-koma work "Sorry, Mama": The lively day-to-day family life of the young boy Yabo Onishi, his mother, and his father. Frequently, they are tempted by their desires (represented as their other selves, with devil horns and tails), and sometimes, against their better judgment, they may fall to them. But above all, they value family the most.

---
**Volume 273 of the Osamu Tezuka Complete Works**"},"links":{"al":"57687","amz":"https://www.amazon.co.jp/-/en/%E6%89%8B%E5%A1%9A%E6%B2%BB%E8%99%AB-ebook/dp/B00JPXERCA/ref=tmm_kin_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&qid=1652672398&sr=8-1","ap":"mako-to-rumi-to-chii","bw":"de711a1090-4b2f-495b-bc96-fba4197be8d7","cdj":"https://www.cdjapan.co.jp/product/NEOBK-192064?s_ssid=e4599b6281c799fb54","ebj":"https://ebookjapan.yahoo.co.jp/books/100490/","kt":"21293","mal":"27687","mu":"66697"},"originalLanguage":"ja","publicationDemographic":"josei","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"36fd93ea-e8b8-445e-b836-358f02b3d33d","name":{"en":"Monsters"}},{"id":"423e2eae-a7a2-4a8b-ac03-a8351462d71d","name":{"en":"Romance"}},{"id":"4d32cc48-9f00-4cca-9b5a-a839f0764984","name":{"en":"Comedy"}},{"id":"b9af3a63-f058-46de-a9a0-e0c13906197a","name":{"en":"Drama"}},{"id":"caaa44eb-cd40-4177-b930-79d3ef2afe87","name":{"en":"School Life"}},{"id":"da2d50ca-3018-4cc0-ac7a-6b7d472a29ea","name":{"en":"Delinquents"}},{"id":"e5301a23-ebd9-49dd-a0cb-2add944c7fe9","name":{"en":"Slice of Life"}}]}

:::{"id":"f195f197-03a4-450f-8c23-5340d75d5029","title":{"en":"The Evil Sorceress Plans to Survive!"},"altTitles":[{"en":"Evil Sorceress' Survival Strategy"},{"zh-ro":"Fǎnpài Monǚ Zì Jiù Jìhuà"},{"zh-ro":"Fanpai Monü Zi Jiu Jihua"},{"zh-ro":"Fanpai Monu Zi Jiu Jihua"},{"zh":"反派魔女自救计划"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["en","fr","pt-br","pl","id"],"relatedIdds":["106826b5-a7ab-4f32-b4fa-01424bf46b18","44c5af9f-ddfe-4f74-948f-fa8930495925"],"description":{"en":"Xiao Yao, a young lady of a wealthy, respectable family in the 21st century, thought her life had ended when she passed away due to a deadly illness. However, she opened her eyes and found herself in the body of a manhua's villainess, Princess Abella.  
  
Despite not having any magic powers nor capabilities, the pompous and vicious Princess caused countless people to suffer from her heinous acts. Her greed for the throne even led her to murder her own father, thus sentencing her to death while the protagonists of the manhua lived happily ever.  
  
With a second chance at life in such a healthy body, Xiao Yao will not sit back idly while the Princess' impending doom befalls her again. This time, she will strive to change the Princess' fate, and along the way, will attempt to discover her hidden secrets and of those around her…  


---","fr":"Xiao Yao, une jeune femme d'une famille riche et respectable au 21ème siècle, pensait que sa vie avait pris fin quand elle est décédée à cause d'une maladie mortelle. Cependant, elle ouvrit les yeux et se retrouva dans le corps de la méchante d'un manhua, la princesse Abella.  
  
En dépit de ne pas avoir de pouvoirs magiques ni de capacités, la princesse pompeuse et vicieuse a fait souffrir d'innombrables personnes de ses actes odieux. Son avidité pour le trône l'a même amenée à assassiner son propre père, la condamnant ainsi à mort alors que les protagonistes du manhua vivaient heureux pour toujours.  
  
Avec une seconde chance à la vie dans uncorps sain, Xiao Yao ne va pas rester les bras croisés tandis que le destin imminent de la princesse la menace à nouveau. :::{"id":"f1b0052a-6290-4c9b-b6ef-a9c8dbe9ed61","title":{"en":"I Might Be A Fake Cultivator"},"altTitles":[{"zh":"我修的可能是假仙"},{"zh-ro":"Wo Xiu De Keneng Shi Jia Xian"},{"ko":"사기당해서 신선이 되었습니다"},{"ru":"Фальшивый культиватор выбранный богом"},{"en":"Cultivation, Kidding Me!"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["fr","pt-br","en"],"description":{"en":"It's a cultivation story. One with immortal gods and cultivation arts. But more importantly, it's the story of a boy named An Lin, a mortal who was heavily in debt and was pursued by loan sharks before meeting his savior, a True God.
Saved from the loan sharks, An Lin was sent to cultivate at the Immortal Cultivation United University, but it seems like he was trolled by the True God...? Is this really the life he was expecting? Wasn't this just a regular cultivation story? What's that? I might be a fake cultivator?","ko":"어머니가 돌아가시고 이제 막 대학교에 입학한 내가 아버지의 도박 빚을 떠안게 되었다. 
오늘도 어김없이 빚쟁이들에게 쫓기던 중 실수로 건물에서 추락하고 마는데... 이렇게 죽나 싶었던 바로 그 순간! 
신선이 나타나 목숨을 구해주는 것은 물론, 새로이 인생을 시작할 수 있는 전신(戰神) 시스템까지 선물해주었다.
내게 수선할 자질이 있다고 말하는 어르신의 말을 믿어도 되는 걸까? 인간세상을 떠나 수선세계로 가면 지금보다 나은 생활을 할 수 있을까...? 

하지만 어째서 사기 당한 것 같은 느낌이 들지?!","zh":"嫦娥仙子为何半夜飙歌，七仙女为何夜偷蟠桃，各方神兽为何屡遭黑手，数百名仙人集体跳广场舞的背后又隐藏着什么？这一切的背后，是神仙的抽疯还是道德的沦丧？让我们跟随漫画，走进修了假仙的安林的内心世界，开启探索与发现之旅！"},"links":{"al":"120284","ap":"i-might-be-a-fake-cultivator","engtl":"https://www.webnovel.com/comic/i-might-be-a-fake-cultivator_16161044605047501","mu":"164446","nu":"i-might-be-a-fake-cultivator","raw":"https://ac.qq.com/Comic/ComicInfo/id/641908"},"originalLanguage":"zh","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"391b0423-d847-456f-aff0-8b0cfc03066b","name":{"en":"Action"}},{"id":"3e2b8dae-350e-4ab8-a8ce-016e844b9f0d","name":{"en":"Long Strip"}},{"id":"4d32cc48-9f00-4cca-9b5a-a839f0764984","name":{"en":"Comedy"}},{"id":"87cc87cd-a395-47af-b27a-93258283bbc6","name":{"en":"Adventure"}},{"id":"acc803a4-c95a-4c22-86fc-eb6b582d82a2","name":{"en":"Wuxia"}},{"id":"cdc58593-87dd-415e-bbc0-2ec27bf404cc","name":{"en":"Fantasy"}},{"id":"e197df38-d0e7-43b5-9b09-2842d0c326dd","name":{"en":"Web Comic"}},{"id":"f4122d1c-3b44-44d0-9936-ff7502c39ad3","name":{"en":"Adaptation"}},{"id":"f5ba408b-0e7a-484d-8d49-4e9125ac96de","name":{"en":"Full Color"}}]}

“…I am this pig?”

I open my eyes, and it’s Murim?
I am Yu Shin Un, the ruffian of Baek Un Clan?
A chaotic situation with no time to rest.
In the midst of incoming death!

“You guys have no idea who I am?”

Necromancy from former life.
Martial arts from current life.
He who wields both power!
Now shakes the destiny of the World!]","ko":"sss급 헌터 강태하
치열한 싸움 끝에 결국 죽음을 맞이했다.
그런데...
"이 돼지가 나라고?"
눈을 떠보니 무림이었고, 백운표국의 망나니 유신운이 되어있었다.
혼란스러운 죽음의 위기 속에!

:::{"id":"f1fe6280-7df6-4cc4-9b83-afcefea1d68c","title":{"en":"Ringo Hoppe no Koi"},"altTitles":[{"ja-ro":"24 Ko no Kurisumasu"},{"en":"24 Pieces of Christmas"},{"ja":"24個のクリスマス"},{"en":"Apple-Cheek Love"},{"en":"Blushing Love"},{"ja":"りんごほっぺの恋"},{"zh":"苹果脸之恋"},{"zh-hk":"蘋果臉之戀"}],"lastChapter":"3","availableTranslatedLanguages":["en"],"description":{"en":"A collection of short stories:  
  
#1: Ringo Hoppe no Koi  
Takami has a HUGE problem! She blushes at the drop of a hat, so everyone knows what she is thinking! She finally makes a decision to stop letting her fear of embarrassment control her – she gets a job where her crush is working so that she can confess her feelings to him… but then things go awry in an unexpected way!  
  
#2: Hinatabokko no Heya  
Tomo and Daisuke have been childhood friends for ten years. Whenever something goes wrong with Daisuke, he finds refuge in Tomo's sunshine-abundant room. When Tomo asks Daisuke for a 'date' with him as her birthday present, will the equations of their relationship change?  
  
#3: 24 Ko no Kurisumasu (24 Pieces of Christmas)  
Rio met Ian, the son of her father's friend, during Christmas when she was in the third grade. Ian turned out to be a devil with an angelic smile. That Christmas remains as an irritating memory for Rio, considering how Ian played multiple pranks on her and bullied her throughout the day. After that Christmas, Ian's family moved away to England and she didn't get to see him since then. But Ian sends Christmas cards for her every year. Years later, during Rio's 17th Christmas, Ian is back in Japan……planning some new pranks?"},"links":{"al":"33775","ap":"ringo-hoppe-no-koi","kt":"8352","mal":"3775","mu":"3925"},"originalLanguage":"ja","publicationDemographic":"shoujo","contentRating":"safe","tags":[{"id":"423e2eae-a7a2-4a8b-ac03-a8351462d71d","name":{"en":"Romance"}},{"id":"51d83883-4103-437c-b4b1-731cb73d786c","name":{"en":"Anthology"}},{"id":"b9af3a63-f058-46de-a9a0-e0c13906197a","name":{"en":"Drama"}}]}

:::{"id":"f2259673-b904-4f14-92f3-b8fc20a82ae1","title":{"en":"A Most Virtuous Villain"},"altTitles":[{"ko":"악당의 미학"},{"ko-ro":"Agdang-eui Mihag"},{"en":"The Villain's Aesthetics"},{"en":"A Villain's Aesthetic"},{"en":"Aesthetics of the Villain"},{"id":"Estetika Sang Penjahat"},{"th":"สุนทรียศาสตร์ของจอมวายร้าย"},{"zh":"反派美学"},{"ja":"悪党の美学"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["en","hu"],"description":{"en":"One day, while eating chicken, Sehyeon was transported into the novel she had written in the spur of a moment. She immediately became the idiotic princess, Ione. What else would happen today that would influence the fate of Ione's life and death? In order to survive, she had to make sure the Emperor wasn't killed! As she dashed away to prevent the incident, she ran straight into a man. A man loosely gripping a sword dripping with blood. Nickname: King Regent Kimchi Real name: Aenard Ibn Bonaparte. "You're an author?" She was screwed. The first thing she had to encounter just happened to be a villain who knew how to read her mind! "I'm the only person who knows that I can read minds." Sehyun's breathing quickened. "So, who are you?" A tight-knit fantasy romance with a menacing villain!

---
Becoming a princess in a fantasy world might be the dream of many, but not for Sehyun Ji, who just enjoys writing her dark and depraved novel. That is, until one day she suddenly wakes up inside the world of her creation! She becomes Princess Ione, the emperor’s daughter destined to die a tragic death. Determined to change her fate, she tries to stop Aenard Bonaparte, the main villain of her novel, from murdering the emperor... and fails. But what’s worse, he can read her mind! Will Sehyun—now Princess Ione—manage to survive?

Chika, an upcoming model, saves Sagiri while she's being harassed by a guy in the street, and Sagiri is so mad that he bribed the guy to leave that she insists on paying her schoolmate back…  
  
-The Hallway Rumors  
"Wherever you are.. I will always find you," thinks Kooko about Akihiro, one of her guy friends, whom she likes. She is tasked to help the sleepless emperor, who was cursed by a witch, by using her ability to induce sleep whenever she touches another person's body with her lips. Can Lilian survive being with the emperor, ‘Kael Rue Kaldorf?'

---
Reincarnated as the illegitimate daughter of Duke McKellion, Lilian was never fully embraced by her father or society. So, when she has the opportunity to take her sister’s place in an arranged marriage to Emperor Kael Lu Kaldorf, Lilian jumps at the chance. 

The only problem is, her prospective partner gets cranky without his sleep, and since being cursed by a vindictive witch, the tyrannical emperor hasn’t experienced a single moment of slumber. 

But that’s no challenge for Lilian, who possesses the ability to induce sleep with a kiss. Now, tasked with the duty of keeping His Majesty well-rested, Lilian must kiss the emperor each night to keep his temper at bay. It’s a simple contractual agreement, and Lilian has no plans to develop romantic feelings, but what happens when Kael unexpectedly falls for her?

:::{"id":"f27b6921-04d1-4e67-948b-66d7eca54d32","title":{"en":"Lady Cinderella (Promo)"},"altTitles":[{"ko":"레이디 신데렐라"},{"en":"Lady Cindrella (Promo)"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["en","pt-br"],"description":{"en":""I need a fake fiancé to protect me!"

After her mother's death, Elladis (Ella) had fallen from her father's favor and was reduced to being a maid under the abuse of her stepmother and sisters.

But her stepmother wasn't satisfied to treat Ella as her maid, so she forced her to marry a gambling-crazy Viscount.

The only pleasure for Ella, who lives a difficult life, was the country's hero, Archduke Wellington. Ella goes through each day memorizing anything about Archduke Wellington.

However, the Viscount, who is her husband only in name, sells Ella to pay his gambling debts. However, Ella, who runs away with the intention of dying, somehow returns to the age of 18 after a desperate wish.

The opportunity came once again like a miracle!

She decided not to live the way she used to until she inherited her mother's legacy and chose to entrust herself to Archduke Wellington.

"Please save me from this house."

"What can I get in return for saving you?"

"I'll be your fake fiancée."

What will be the conclusion of Ella's bold choice, who proposes a contractual engagement to Archduke Wellington using the information she knows from her previous life as bait?","ko":"“날 지켜 줄 가짜 약혼자가 필요해!”

어머니가 돌아가신 뒤, 계모와 새언니의 구박과 아버지의 방치 아래
백작가의 영애에서 하녀 신세로 전락한 엘레이디스(엘라).

계모는 엘라를 하녀로 부려먹는 것도 모자라 
도박에 미친 자작에게 억지로 시집 보낸다.

힘겨운 삶을 사는 엘라의 유일한 낙은 나라의 영웅, 웰링턴 대공 덕질!
엘라는 웰링턴 대공에 대한 것이라면 무엇이든 달달 외우며 하루하루를 버틴다.

그러나 무늬만 남편이던 사람은 도박빚에 엘라를 팔아 넘기고,
죽을 각오로 도망치던 엘라는 간절한 바람 끝에 18살로 회귀한다.

기적처럼 다시 한번 찾아온 기회!
예전처럼 살지 않기로 다짐한 엘라는 어머니의 유산을 물려받을 때까지
웰링턴 대공에게 자신을 의탁하기로 마음먹는다.

“저를 이 집에서 구해 주세요.”
“그대를 구해 주는 대가로 나는 뭘 얻을 수 있지?”
“제가 각하의 가짜 약혼녀가 되어 드릴게요.”

전생의 덕질로 알고 있는 정보를 미끼로 웰링턴 대공에게 가짜 약혼을 제안한 엘라.
엘라의 당돌한 선택이 불러올 결말은?!

[일러스트] 알터

:::{"id":"f2f87d31-31ed-4f14-a0df-9fb888ebd483","title":{"en":"Peerless Saint Emperor"},"altTitles":[{"en":"Jue Shi Sheng Di"},{"en":"Peerless Emperor"},{"en":"绝世圣帝"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["id","en"],"description":{"en":"In a low-level continent called The Spirit Continent (or Phantom Continent), Zheng Tian was the heir to Huyan Jueluo family, with exceptional talent, and had always been arrogant. Until one day, the Heavenly Palace Azure Dragon Sacred Beast sent out a message that there was a artifact, a magic weapon, and the nine star skill in the Spirit continent. Alicia decisively rejects the heroine's role as "nonsense." Taking the name "Aria" as an adventurer, she gradually grows into the "Ash-crowned Princess of Slaughter" who wields multiple weapons and magic!

But, when she receives a request to escort a "villainess," without realizing it she finds herself caught up in the stage of the game where nobles struggle against each other...?

"I am 'me.' I'm not a character in a game!"","ja":"剣と魔法の世界シエルで孤児として生きていた少女アーリシア。
ある日、彼女は自分が“乙女ゲームのヒロイン”であると知ってしまう。
両親の死さえ単にストーリーの一部だったのだ。
アーリシアはヒロインの役割を「くだらない」と一刀両断すると、冒険者『アリア』を名乗り、次第に複数の武器と魔法を操る「殺戮（さつりく）の灰かぶり姫」へと成長していく！
だが、“悪役令嬢”の護衛依頼を受けたことで、気付かぬ間に貴族同士が争うゲームの舞台に巻き込まれていき――？
「私は“私”だ。ゲームの登場人物じゃない！」
武器を作れ！　技を鍛えろ！
強敵との戦いに生き残り、乙女ゲームをぶち壊せ！
戦うヒロインが魅せる、壮絶＆爽快な異世界バトルファンタジー！

Before my rebirth, I'd been used for the past 400 years as the empire's sword. And so, I swore to destroy the empire. I found the young prince of the country and became his teacher. I taught him how to become a tyrant and asked for the country.

"I will do as the lady wishes."

He conquered the whole empire for me, and I ran away.

"I came to take you, Charlize Ronan," Dylan had become a perfect tyrant and searched the entire empire for me.

"You tamed me, so why did you run away?"

---
All Charlize Ronan ever wanted was to bring honor to her family. But instead, she is forced into becoming a “living sword” -- a mere tool for the emperors. It is from this hell that she prays for justice… and awakens in her former body. Now, determined to tear down this horrible empire, Charlize seeks out the young prince, Dylan Blade. She will put him on the throne, not as an honorable ruler, but as a tyrant. It is time for Charlize to tame the one who will bring forth her revenge.

:::{"id":"f3d3cf42-a12a-42f5-bd56-70b587eee06a","title":{"en":"An Introvert's Hookup Hiccups: This Gyaru Is Head Over Heels for Me!"},"altTitles":[{"ja":"陰キャの僕に罰ゲームで告白してきたはずのギャルが、どう見ても僕にベタ惚れです"},{"ja-ro":"Inkya no Boku ni Batsu Game ni Kokuhaku Shitekita Hazu no Gyaru ga, Doumitemo Boku ni Betahore Desu"},{"zh-hk":"因懲罰遊戲才向陰角的我告白的辣妹，怎麼看都已經完全迷戀上我了"},{"en":"The Gal Who Was Meant to Confess to Me as a Game Punishment Has Apparently Fallen in Love with Me"},{"en":"An Introvert's Hookup Hiccups: This Gyaru Is Head Over Heels for Me!"}],"availableTranslatedLanguages":["en","fr","es-la","tr","pt-br"],"description":{"en":"When the gorgeous Nanami Barato confesses to Yoshin Misumai, it seems too good to be true! Only, it is—and Yoshin knows it. How’s an introverted guy like him supposed to keep his cool when he knows this is all just a dare? Even more puzzling, despite her gaudy appearance, this supposed gyaru isn’t actually all that good with guys!
